Elizabeth Akosua Tiwaah靠oh bụ onye Belgian mara mma nke e kpuwere okpueze dị ka Miss Earth Belgium 2015 na onye nnọchi anya Belgium na Miss Earth 2015
Ọ bụ Miss Exclusive 2014, Emily Vanhoutte kpuwere ya okpueze.
Elizabeth sonyeere Miss Exclusive 2015 wee kpọsaa ya dị ka onye mmeri
Ndị gbara ọsọ ya gụnyere Axelle Stratsaert dị ka onye gbara ọsọ nke mbụ ebe Amy De Paepe kpọpụtara na ọzọ nke abụọ.
